title: VT English｜全新單元震撼登場

json.text: Hi, everyone! Welcome to VT English! I'm your host, Kelsi!
In this new video series, we're going to be teaching you fun and useful English!
VoiceTube TV is going to be putting out a new English video series!
Every Tuesday, we'll be putting out a video.
There will be plenty of interesting topics to help you learn commonly used English!
So, look out for our first video next Tuesday!
And don't forget to subscribe and turn on your notifications so that you don't miss any of our videos!
